{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "64cc30e8-73a1-48ad-a8e8-70a9195d579b",
		"name": "regula-hub",
		"description": "Collection for the regula-hub microservice — a FastAPI wrapper around SisReg III.\n\n**Quick Start:**\n1. Set the `api_key` collection variable with a valid API key\n2. Run requests in order: Health → Raw Videofonista → Sync\n\n**Authentication:** All endpoints (except `/health`) require an `X-API-Key` header. Set the `api_key` collection variable.\n\nGenerate an API key with:\n```\npython -c \"import secrets; print(secrets.token_urlsafe(32))\"\n```\n\n**Endpoint Groups:**\n- **Health** — Service health and dependency checks (no auth required)\n- **Raw (Videofonista)** — SisReg pass-through endpoints (dd/MM/yyyy dates)\n- **Sync (Pipeline)** — Integration pipeline status, appointments, and manual trigger (ISO dates)\n\n**Date Formats:**\n- Raw Videofonista: `dd/MM/yyyy` (use `{{date_initial}}` and `{{date_final}}` variables)\n- Sync endpoints: `YYYY-MM-DD` (use `{{iso_date}}` variable)",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:8000",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "appointment_code",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "date_initial",
			"value": "09/03/2026",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "Start date in dd/MM/yyyy format for raw Videofonista endpoints"
		},
		{
			"key": "date_final",
			"value": "09/03/2026",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "End date in dd/MM/yyyy format for raw Videofonista endpoints"
		},
		{
			"key": "iso_date",
			"value": "2026-03-09",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "Date in YYYY-MM-DD format for regulation endpoints"
		},
		{
			"key": "api_key",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string",
			"description": "API key for X-API-Key header. Generate with: python -c \"import secrets; print(secrets.token_urlsafe(32))\""
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Health",
			"description": "Service health and dependency checks.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Health Check",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Service is healthy', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json.status).to.eql('healthy');",
									"    pm.expect(json.service).to.eql('regula-hub');",
									"    pm.expect(json.checks.sisreg_reachable.status).to.eql('healthy');",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Has version and uptime', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json.version).to.be.a('string');",
									"    pm.expect(json.uptime_seconds).to.be.a('number');",
									"    pm.expect(json.timestamp).to.be.a('string');",
									"});"
								]
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"health"
							]
						},
						"description": "Returns the overall service health status, version, uptime, and dependency checks (SisReg III reachability).\n\n**Status Codes:**\n- `200` — Service is healthy\n- `503` — Service is unhealthy (SisReg unreachable)"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Healthy",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "GET",
								"header": [],
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{base_url}}/health",
									"host": [
										"{{base_url}}"
									],
									"path": [
										"health"
									]
								}
							},
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"body": "{\n  \"status\": \"healthy\",\n  \"service\": \"regula-hub\",\n  \"version\": \"0.1.0\",\n  \"uptime_seconds\": 42.0,\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-09T10:30:45.123456+00:00\",\n  \"checks\": {\n    \"sisreg_reachable\": {\n      \"status\": \"healthy\",\n      \"latency_ms\": 142.5,\n      \"detail\": null\n    }\n  }\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "Unhealthy",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "GET",
