		{
			"name": "Raw (Videofonista)",
			"description": "Raw SisReg endpoints using Videofonista profile (state-wide view). Pass-through 1:1 mapping of SisReg CGI functionality.\n\nAll endpoints require X-API-Key header.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Videofonista - List Appointments",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status 200', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response has appointments array', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json.appointments).to.be.an('array');",
									"    pm.expect(json.total).to.be.a('number');",
									"    pm.expect(json.total).to.eql(json.appointments.length);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response has pagination fields', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(json.current_page).to.be.a('number');",
									"    pm.expect(json.current_page).to.be.at.least(1);",
									"    pm.expect(json.total_pages).to.be.a('number');",
									"    pm.expect(json.total_pages).to.be.at.least(1);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Save first appointment code for detail', function () {",
									"    var json = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (json.appointments.length > 0) {",
									"        var code = json.appointments[0].code;",
									"        pm.collectionVariables.set('appointment_code', code);",
									"        console.log('Saved appointment_code: ' + code);",
									"    }",
									"});"
								]
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "X-API-Key",
								"value": "{{api_key}}",
								"description": "API key for authentication"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/raw/videofonista/appointments?dt_inicial={{date_initial}}&dt_final={{date_final}}&cmb_situacao=7",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"raw",
								"videofonista",
								"appointments"
							],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "dt_inicial",
									"value": "{{date_initial}}",
									"description": "Start date in dd/MM/yyyy format (required)"
								},
								{
									"key": "dt_final",
									"value": "{{date_final}}",
									"description": "End date in dd/MM/yyyy format (required)"
								},
								{
									"key": "tipo_periodo",
									"value": "A",
									"description": "Period type: S=Solicitation, A=Scheduling, E=Execution, P=Pending, C=Cancellation (default: A)",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "cmb_situacao",
									"value": "7",
									"description": "Status filter 1-12 (default: 7 = Scheduled/Pending/Executed)"
								},
								{
									"key": "qtd_itens_pag",
									"value": "0",
									"description": "Items per page: 10, 20, 50, 100, 0=all (default: 0)",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "pagina",
									"value": "0",
									"description": "Page number, 0-based (default: 0)",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "ordenacao",
									"value": "2",
									"description": "Sort order (default: 2)",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "co_solicitacao",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Filter by appointment code",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "cns_paciente",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Filter by patient CNS",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "no_usuario",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Filter by patient name",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "cnes_solicitante",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Filter by requesting unit CNES",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "cnes_executante",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Filter by executing unit CNES",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "co_proc_unificado",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Filter by unified procedure code",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "co_pa_interno",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Filter by internal procedure code",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "ds_procedimento",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Filter by procedure description",
									"disabled": true
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Lists appointments using the Videofonista profile (state-wide view) — pass-through 1:1 with SisReg CGI.\n\nAll query parameters map directly to SisReg form fields. Uses the main SISREG_USERNAME/SISREG_PASSWORD credentials.\n\n**Required Parameters:**\n- `dt_inicial` — Start date in `dd/MM/yyyy` format\n- `dt_final` — End date in `dd/MM/yyyy` format\n\n**Optional Parameters (with defaults):**\n- `tipo_periodo` (default `A`) — Period type (S/A/E/P/C)\n- `cmb_situacao` (default `7`) — Status filter (1-12)\n- `qtd_itens_pag` (default `0`) — Items per page (10/20/50/100/0=all)\n- `pagina` (default `0`) — Page number (0-based)\n- `ordenacao` (default `2`) — Sort order\n\n**Optional Filters (empty by default):**\n- `co_solicitacao` — Appointment code\n- `cns_paciente` — Patient CNS\n- `no_usuario` — Patient name\n- `cnes_solicitante` — Requesting unit CNES\n- `cnes_executante` — Executing unit CNES\n- `co_proc_unificado` — Unified procedure code\n- `co_pa_interno` — Internal procedure code\n- `ds_procedimento` — Procedure description\n\n**Response includes pagination:** `current_page` (1-based) and `total_pages`.\n\n**Status Codes:**\n- `200` — Success\n- `401` — Invalid SisReg credentials\n- `422` — Invalid parameter format\n- `503` — SisReg session expired after retries"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "Success — 1 appointment",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "GET",
								"header": [
									{
										"key": "X-API-Key",
										"value": "{{api_key}}",
										"description": "API key for authentication"
									}
								],
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{base_url}}/raw/videofonista/appointments?dt_inicial=09/03/2026&dt_final=09/03/2026&cmb_situacao=7",
									"host": [
										"{{base_url}}"
									],
									"path": [
										"raw",
										"videofonista",
										"appointments"
									],
									"query": [
										{
											"key": "dt_inicial",
											"value": "09/03/2026"
										},
										{
											"key": "dt_final",
											"value": "09/03/2026"
										},
										{
											"key": "cmb_situacao",
											"value": "7"
										}
									]
								}
							},
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"header": [
								{
									"key": "Content-Type",
									"value": "application/json"
								}
							],
							"body": "{\n  \"appointments\": [\n    {\n      \"code\": \"1234567890\",\n      \"request_date\": \"09/03/2026\",\n      \"risk\": 0,\n      \"patient\": \"JOAO DA SILVA\",\n      \"age\": \"45\",\n      \"procedure\": \"TELECONSULTA EM CARDIOLOGIA\",\n      \"cid\": \"I10\",\n      \"department_solicitation\": \"UBS CENTRO\",\n      \"department_execute\": \"HOSPITAL REGIONAL\",\n      \"status_sisreg\": \"AGE/PEN/EXEC\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 1,\n  \"current_page\": 1,\n  \"total_pages\": 1\n}"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Videofonista - Appointment Detail",
